																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "hc5ceaa73gea5dg4bebga829g889508d02558",
																	"value": "He began worshipping Shar and raised an army of Dark Justiciars right underneath the locals' noses. A coalition of Harpers and druids put him down - killed him and buried him in the Thorm family mausoleum. ",
