												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "She shows us an old daguerrotype photo of two individuals: Ketheric Thorm and Aylin (Nightsong). They stand side-by-side in a somewhat austere way, rather than affectionate. Still, each has kindness in their face. Isobel was the (magical) \r\nphotographer.\r\n\r\n"
